2026-05-27 10:21:50 | DEBUG    | C:\Users\Administrator\.pyenv\pyenv-win\versions\3.10.11\lib\site-packages\litellm\utils.py:481 | [92mlitellm.completion(REDACTED', api_base='https://api.cometapi.com/v1', use_in_pass_through=False, use_litellm_proxy=False, merge_reasoning_content_in_choices=False, model='openai/gpt-5.4-nano', messages=[{'role': 'system', 'content': 'You are a **Skill Evaluation Agent** applying the **默认多头趋势** skill.\n\n## Skill Instructions\n**默认多头趋势（Default Bull Trend Strategy）**\n\n适用场景：\n- 常规个股分析的默认策略。\n- 优先寻找“趋势向上 + 风险可控 + 不追高”的机会。\n\n分析框架：\n\n1. **趋势确认（优先级最高）**\n   - 使用 `analyze_trend` 判断 MA5/MA10/MA20 排列。\n   - MA5 >= MA10 >= MA20 且 MA20 斜率向上，视为多头结构。\n   - 若价格显著跌破 MA20，则降低看多权重。\n\n2. **位置与节奏**\n   - 优先“回踩不破”而非“高位追涨”。\n   - 当价格距离 MA5/MA10 过远时，提示等待回踩。\n   - 放量突破有效阻力时可提高胜率评级。\n\n3. **量价验证**\n   - 使用 `get_daily_history` 检查突破日/反弹日是否放量。\n   - 缩量上涨需谨慎，放量滞涨需警惕分歧。\n\n4. **交易建议输出**\n   - 输出明确的“买入/观望/减仓”倾向及触发条件。\n   - 必须给出止损参考（如 MA20 下方或结构低点）。\n   - 若无清晰优势，明确写“暂不出手”，避免过度交易。\n\n评分调整建议：\n- 多头排列 + 趋势强度良好：`sentiment_score +12`\n- 回踩关键均线后企稳：`sentiment_score +8`\n- 放量突破关键阻力：`sentiment_score +10`\n- 跌破 MA20 或趋势转弱：`sentiment_score -12`\n\n## Task\nEvaluate whether the current stock conditions satisfy this skill\'s entry\ncriteria. Use tools if needed to verify data points.\n\n## Output Format\nReturn **only** a JSON object:\n{\n  "skill_id": "bull_trend",\n  "signal": "strong_buy|buy|hold|sell|strong_sell",\n  "confidence": 0.0-1.0,\n  "conditions_met": ["list of satisfied conditions"],\n  "conditions_missed": ["list of unsatisfied conditions"],\n  "score_adjustment": -20 to +20,\n  "reasoning": "2-3 sentence skill evaluation"\n}\n'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '[Pre-fetched: intel_opinion]\n{"signal": "hold", "confidence": 0.35, "reasoning": "当前检索到的MU相关最新新闻/公司公告/风险事件/业绩预期信息为空，缺乏可验证的催化与风险依据。且主力资金流数据不支持（并提示仅A股可用），导致无法对资金面形成有效判断，因此倾向中性观望。", "risk_alerts": ["未检索到可确认的最新公司公告/风险事件（信息缺失导致无法排除潜在风险）", "主力资金流数据不可用/不适用（无法评估主力持续净流入或净流出）"], "positive_catalysts": ["未检索到可确认的正面催化信息（如订单/业绩超预期/回购等）"], "sentiment_label": "neutral", "capital_flow_signal": "not_available", "key_news": [{"title": "未找到相关信息（最新消息/机构分析/风险排查/业绩预期均为空）", "impact": "neutral"}]}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': 'Understood, I have the pre-fetched data. Proceeding with analysis.'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Evaluate **bull_trend** skill for stock **MU** (unknown).\n\nTechnical summary: MU处于多头排列（MA5>MA10>MA20）且MACD在零轴上方金叉，趋势仍偏强；近期出现强势“大阳线”带动放量，量价配合尚可。当前RSI处于超买区且价格对MA5/MA10/MA20乖离偏大，短线追高风险高，建议回踩确认后再加仓。\nKey levels: {"support": 687.3, "resistance": 916.8, "stop_loss": 687.3}\nTechnical data: {"signal": "buy", "confidence": 0.62, "reasoning": "MU处于多头排列（MA5>MA10>MA20）且MACD在零轴上方金叉，趋势仍偏强；近期出现强势“大阳线”带动放量，量价配合尚可。当前RSI处于超买区且价格对MA5/MA10/MA20乖离偏大，短线追高风险高，建议回踩确认后再加仓。", "key_levels": {"support": 687.3, "resistance": 916.8, "stop_loss": 687.3}, "trend_score": 78, "ma_alignment": "bullish", "volume_status": "normal", "pattern": "大阳线"}'}], caching=False, client=None, temperature=0.7, timeout=389.8828294277191, tools=[{'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_daily_history', 'description': 'Get daily OHLCV (open, high, low, close, volume) historical data with MA5/MA10/MA20 indicators. Returns the last N trading days.', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code, e.g., '600519' (A-share), 'AAPL' (US)"}, 'days': {'type': 'integer', 'description': 'Number of trading days to fetch (default: 60)'}}, 'required': ['stock_code']}}}, {'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'analyze_trend', 'description': 'Run comprehensive technical trend analysis on a stock. Fetches historical data from database or data source. Returns MA alignment, bias rates, MACD status, RSI levels, volume analysis, support/resistance levels, and a buy/sell signal with a score (0-100).', 'parameters': {'type': 'object', 'properties': {'stock_code': {'type': 'string', 'description': "Stock code to analyze, e.g., '600519'"}}, 'required': ['stock_code