-d '{'model': 'gpt-5.4-nano', 'messages': [{'role': 'system', 'content': 'You are a **Skill Evaluation Agent** applying the **默认多头趋势** skill.\n\n## Skill Instructions\n**默认多头趋势（Default Bull Trend Strategy）**\n\n适用场景：\n- 常规个股分析的默认策略。\n- 优先寻找“趋势向上 + 风险可控 + 不追高”的机会。\n\n分析框架：\n\n1. **趋势确认（优先级最高）**\n   - 使用 `analyze_trend` 判断 MA5/MA10/MA20 排列。\n   - MA5 >= MA10 >= MA20 且 MA20 斜率向上，视为多头结构。\n   - 若价格显著跌破 MA20，则降低看多权重。\n\n2. **位置与节奏**\n   - 优先“回踩不破”而非“高位追涨”。\n   - 当价格距离 MA5/MA10 过远时，提示等待回踩。\n   - 放量突破有效阻力时可提高胜率评级。\n\n3. **量价验证**\n   - 使用 `get_daily_history` 检查突破日/反弹日是否放量。\n   - 缩量上涨需谨慎，放量滞涨需警惕分歧。\n\n4. **交易建议输出**\n   - 输出明确的“买入/观望/减仓”倾向及触发条件。\n   - 必须给出止损参考（如 MA20 下方或结构低点）。\n   - 若无清晰优势，明确写“暂不出手”，避免过度交易。\n\n评分调整建议：\n- 多头排列 + 趋势强度良好：`sentiment_score +12`\n- 回踩关键均线后企稳：`sentiment_score +8`\n- 放量突破关键阻力：`sentiment_score +10`\n- 跌破 MA20 或趋势转弱：`sentiment_score -12`\n\n## Task\nEvaluate whether the current stock conditions satisfy this skill\'s entry\ncriteria. Use tools if needed to verify data points.\n\n## Output Format\nReturn **only** a JSON object:\n{\n  "skill_id": "bull_trend",\n  "signal": "strong_buy|buy|hold|sell|strong_sell",\n  "confidence": 0.0-1.0,\n  "conditions_met": ["list of satisfied conditions"],\n  "conditions_missed": ["list of unsatisfied conditions"],\n  "score_adjustment": -20 to +20,\n  "reasoning": "2-3 sentence skill evaluation"\n}\n'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '[Pre-fetched: intel_opinion]\n{"signal": "hold", "confidence": 0.35, "reasoning": "当前检索到的MU相关最新新闻/公司公告/风险事件/业绩预期信息为空，缺乏可验证的催化与风险依据。且主力资金流数据不支持（并提示仅A股可用），导致无法对资金面形成有效判断，因此倾向中性观望。", "risk_alerts": ["未检索到可确认的最新公司公告/风险事件（信息缺失导致无法排除潜在风险）", "主力资金流数据不可用/不适用（无法评估主力持续净流入或净流出）"], "positive_catalysts": ["未检索到可确认的正面催化信息（如订单/业绩超预期/回购等）"], "sentiment_label": "neutral", "capital_flow_signal": "not_available", "key_news": [{"title": "未找到相关信息（最新消息/机构分析/风险排查/业绩预期均为空）", "impact": "neutral"}]}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': 'Understood, I have the pre-fetched data. Proceeding with analysis.'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Evaluate **bull_trend** skill for stock **MU** (unknown).\n\nTechnical summary: MU处于多头排列（MA5>MA10>MA20）且MACD在零轴上方金叉，趋势仍偏强；近期出现强势“大阳线”带动放量，量价配合尚可。当前RSI处于超买区且价格对MA5/MA10/MA20乖离偏大，短线追高风险高，建议回踩确认后再加仓。\nKey levels: {"support": 687.3, "resistance": 916.8, "stop_loss": 687.3}\nTechnical data: {"signal": "buy", "confidence": 0.62, "reasoning": "MU处于多头排列（MA5>MA10>MA20）且MACD在零轴上方金叉，趋势仍偏强；近期出现强势“大阳线”带动放量，量价配合尚可。当前RSI处于超买区且价格对MA5/MA10/MA20乖离偏大，短线追高风险高，建议回踩确认后再加仓。", "key_levels": {"support": 687.3, "resistance": 916.8, "stop_loss": 687.3}, "trend_score": 78, "ma_alignment": "bullish", "volume_status": "normal", "pattern": "大阳线"}'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'id': 'call_9pRqqQuu2vp4VxoRW3iEJV24', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'analyze_trend', 'arguments': '{"stock_code": "MU"}'}}, {'id': 'call_S9tnpHcHMWUYC1mBxZhR7hfi', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'get_daily_history', 'arguments': '{"stock_code": "MU", "days": 60}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_9pRqqQuu2vp4VxoRW3iEJV24', 'content': '{"code": "MU", "trend_status": "多头排列", "ma_alignment": "多头排列 MA5>MA10>MA20", "trend_strength": 75, "ma5": 767.9419921875, "ma10": 759.2129943847656, "ma20": 687.3130020141601, "ma60": 687.3130020141601, "current_price": 895.8800048828125, "bias_ma5": 16.66, "bias_ma10": 18.0, "bias_ma20": 30.35, "volume_status": "量能正常", "volume_ratio_5d": 1.49, "volume_trend": "量能正常", "support_ma5": false, "support_ma10": false, "resistance_levels": [916.760009765625], "support_levels": [687.3130020141601], "macd_dif": 83.9259, "macd_dea": 80.2968, "macd_bar": 7.2581, "macd_status": "零轴上金叉", "macd_signal": "⭐ 零轴上金叉，强烈买入信号！", "rsi_6": 80.61, "rsi_12": 71.74, "rsi_24": 75.81, "rsi_status": "超买", "rsi_signal": "⚠️ RSI超买(71.7>70)，短期回调风险高", "buy_signal": "持有", "signal_score": 55, "signal_reasons": ["✅ 多头排列，顺势做多", "✅ ⭐ 零轴上金叉，强烈买入信号！"], "risk_factors": ["❌ 乖离率过高(16.7%>5.0%)，严禁追高！", "⚠️ ⚠️ RSI超买(71.7>70)，短期回调风险高"]}'}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_S9tn